72
00:06:42,366 --> 00:06:45,267
But look here, I got money, all right?

73
00:06:45,436 --> 00:06:48,530
See, I'm a mechanic at Wilson’s Auto,
the other side of town.

74
00:06:48,872 --> 00:06:53,605
