02:00:05,317 --> 02:00:07,785
- Yes, ma'am.
- All right.

1644
02:00:10,289 --> 02:00:13,725
Well, the 78's gonna be a parking lot
so we should get going.

1645
02:00:13,893 --> 02:00:17,420
I want everyone to say their goodbyes,
all right? Here. Bye, baby.

1646
02:00:17,596 --> 02:00:19,257
Thank you, Mama.
- You're welcome.

1647
02:00:29,008 --> 02:00:31,033
Why does she always do that?

1648
02:00:31,577 --> 02:00:35,707
She's an onion, Michael. You have to
peel her back a layer at a time.

1649
02:00:38,450 --> 02:00:40,145
Be right back.

1650
02:00:51,297 --> 02:00:53,094
What?

1651
02:00:59,238 --> 02:01:00,262
What, Michael?

1652
02:01:00,806 --> 02:01:03,104
I need a proper hug.

1653
02:01:26,232 --> 02:01:29,724
<i>I read a story the other day
about a boy from the projects.</i>

1654
02:01:30,636 --> 02:01:34,128
<i>No daddy, in and out of foster care.</i>

1655
02:01:34,607 --> 02:01:38,338
<i>He'd been killed in a gang fight
at Hurt Village.</i>

1656
02:01:38,744 --> 02:01:43,204
<i>In the last paragraph, they talked about
his superb athletic skills...</i>

1657
02:01:43,382 --> 02:01:45,475
<i>...and how different
his life might've been...</i>

1658
02:01:45,651 --> 02:01:48,586
<i>...if he hadn't fallen behind
and dropped out of school.</i>

1659
02:01:48,754 --> 02:01:52,349
<i>He was 21 years old the day he died.</i>

1660
02:01:52,524 --> 02:01:54,890
<i>It was his birthday.</i>

1661
02:02:00,165 --> 02:02:02,190
<i>That could have been anyone.</i>

1662
02:02:02,368 --> 02:02:05,201
<i>It could've been my son, Michael.</i>

1663
02:02:05,804 --> 02:02:07,829
<i>But it wasn't.</i>

1664
02:02:10,643 --> 02:02:13,908
<i>And I suppose I have God
to thank for that.</i>

1665
02:02:16,649 --> 02:02:19,914
<i>God and Lawrence Taylor.</i>

1666
02:02:31,096 --> 02:02:32,757
<i>One Mississippi.</i>

1667
02:03:09,601 --> 02:03:15,130
The New England Patriots have traded
the 23rd pick to the Baltimore Ravens.

1668
02:03:15,307 --> 02:03:18,799
And with the 23rd pick
in the 2009 NFL draft...

1669
02:03:18,978 --> 02:03:24,678
...the Baltimore Ravens select Michael
Oher, offensive tackle, Mississippi.
